So if anyone is still using this mod, I finished this <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> patch to change the KD smelter's old behavior to the newer EPL system of requiring <abbr title="Liquid Fuel and Oxidizer">LFO</abbr> for smelting and deleted the older behaviour  

