With that said, I'm also having an issue with the Mobile <abbr title="Vehicle Assembly Building">VAB</abbr> and the pads. I remember this mod had used patch manager for configuration, but nothing is showing in patch manager for KD. Probably related to this, neither the workshops nor the pads are adding the EPL workshop and pad modules, so they are useless. Is someone else having this problem or is it just me?

